<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.1.1">
<l>kaṟavā maṭanā kutaṉkaṉṟuḷḷi ṉāṟpōl</l>
<l>maṟavā taṭiyē ṉuṉṉaiyēyaḻaik kiṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>naṟavār poḻilcūḻ naṟaiyūrniṉṟa nampi</l>
<l>piṟavā maiyeṉaip paṇiyentaipi rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As if a simple, unmilked heifer thinking of its calf,</l>
<l>I, your servant, am calling you without end,</l>
<l>Noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr girded by fragrance-filled groves;</l>
<l>Grant me no rebirth, my father, [my] lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
